  apply hcc
  ¬Ј simpa using ht
  ¬Ј simpa using hx1
  ¬Ј simpa using hx2


/-- **Rate-extraction core** (SW brick W1k): `X^{1вИТg/2} = X¬Јexp(вИТ(g/2)¬Јlog X)` for `X > 0` вАФ turns
    the W1 bound's `X^{ѕГ'}` into the exponential-savings form `X¬Јexp(вИТ(g/2)¬Јlog X)`, whence the SW
