/-!
# The Vinogradov minor-arc sup bound for `вИС ќЫ(n) e(nќ±)` вАФ the complete chain

**Main theorem** (`MinSum.vinogradov_sup`): for `gcd(a,q) = 1`, `|ќ± вИТ a/q| вЙ§ 1/q¬≤`,
`q вЙ• 2`, `U вЙ§ N`, `1 вЙ§ U¬ЈV вЙ§ N`:

  `вАЦвИС_{nвЙ§N} ќЫ(n) e(nќ±)вАЦ вЙ§ BвВБ(U,N,q) + BвВВ(UV,N,q) + V¬Јlog V + BвВД(U,N,q)`

with every `BбµҐ` fully explicit вАФ the analytic heart of the circle method's minor arcs
for almost-all binary Goldbach (`AlmostAllGoldbachReduction.lean` consumes the variance
bound this sup feeds). Built entirely from Mathlib, self-contained in this file.

The chain, bottom to top (every lemma verified 0 errors / 0 sorries with
`#print axioms` = `[propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound]`):

## 1. The min-sum workhorse (Vaughan Lemma 2.2 / IK 13.7)
  вАҐ `image_natCast_Ico`, `image_mul_natCast_Ico` вАФ block bijections onto `ZMod q`.
  вАҐ `sum_Icc_reflect`, `sum_one_div_le`, `sum_q_div_min_le` вАФ the harmonic core.
  вАҐ `dist_round_le` (1-Lipschitz), `dist_round_neg` (even), `dist_int_div_ge` (qвИ§m separation).
  вАҐ `spaced_floor_sign_injOn`, `spaced_min_sum_le` вАФ the ќі-spaced counting core
    (`вИС min(V, 1/(2¬Јdist)) вЙ§ 2V + (2/ќі)(1+log(1/ќі))`).
  вАҐ `block_spaced` вАФ `L вЙ§ q/2` consecutive `h` make `hќ±` pairwise `1/(2q)`-spaced.
  вАҐ `range_min_sum_le` вАФ **the workhorse, uniform-cap form**:
    `вИС_{hвИИ[M,M+R)} min(V, 1/(2вАЦhќ±вАЦ)) вЙ§ (R/(q/2)+1)(2V + 4q(1+log 2q))`.
  вАҐ `dyadic_cap_sum_le` вАФ **the N/h-cap form** via dyadic blocks:
    `вИС_{hвЙ§H} min(N/h, 1/(2вАЦhќ±вАЦ)) вЙ§ (logвВВH+1)(8N/q + 4qL) + 32HL + 4N`.
  вАҐ `cap_symmetric_sum_le` вАФ the symmetric-in-h pure-cap form.

## 2. The exponential-sum chain (self-contained copy of the `MinorArcExpSum.lean` core)
  вАҐ `e`, `e_norm`, `e_pow`, `e_add`, `e_conj`; `geom_exp_bound`, `e_sub_one_norm`,
    `exp_sum_le_sin`, `two_dist_le_abs_sin`, `exp_sum_bound`, `exp_sum_trivial`.
