/-- **The minor-arc `Csup` asymptotic**: for `U=V=P` with `P¬≥ вЙ§ N` and `P¬ЈQ вЙ§ N`,
    `minorCsup вЙ§ 200¬ЈN¬Ј(log N + 2)¬≥/вИЪP` вАФ the `N/вИЪP¬Јpolylog` bound that closes the minor
    LвБі smallness once `P = (log N)^B`, `B вЙ• 8`. -/
lemma minorCsup_bound (N P Q : вДХ) (hP2 : 2 вЙ§ P) (hPN : P ^ 3 вЙ§ N) (hPQ : P * Q вЙ§ N) :
    minorCsup N P P P Q вЙ§ 300 * (N : вДЭ) * (Real.log N + 2) ^ 3 / Real.sqrt P := by
