/-- (A1) Reciprocal-prime form of Dirichlet's theorem вАФ now FULLY PROVEN (below, via
    `A1proof.main`): the residue-class L-series pole at s=1 (`LSeries_residueClass_lower_bound`)
    is transferred through the Chebyshev/FTC partial-summation identity
